description:
In an unprecedented show of strength - the INDIA Block on Monday - led by Rahul Gandhi - pushed back hard against Narendra Modi  & the NDA. Stuff like this has perhaps not been seen in the last 10 years. 
Rahul called out the misuse of Hinduism by BJP / the alleged favouritism by the Speaker / the plight of minorities / the forgotten state of Manipur & the absolute misuse of state machinery. 
Does this mean the green shoots of re-democratisation are here or the BJP will hit back???
